data.title: The KitchenAid® 2-Speed Hand Blender
data.description: The KitchenAid 2-Speed Hand Blender with DC motor - Powerful blending in the palm of your hand. Blend, puree and crush everything from cold smoothies to hot soup to apple sauce with simple, one touch control. Mix and store homemade sauces or baby food purees in the 3-cup BPA free blending jar and lid. The removable 8-inch stainless steel blending arm blends your favorite ingredients in deeper pots while the splash guard increases airflow and helps prevent splashing. Clean up is quick and easy so you have more time to enjoy your creations. Premium performance, exceptional results & legendary KitchenAid quality.

data.title: How Gillette Venus Naked Skin® designed by Braun Intense Pulsed Light Works
data.description:
Gillette Venus Naked Skin® designed by Braun is an intense pulsed light hair removal system that has been clinically tested for at-home use. In other words, you'll get professionally derived intense pulsed light technology at a fraction of the cost.  

Here's how it works: Intense Pulsed Light (or IPL) works its magic beneath the skin's surface by targeting the melanin in dark hair, helping to break the cycle of hair re-growth. With continued, periodic use, the light energy helps prevent unwanted hair from reaching the skin's surface.

data.title: When to Use Gillette Venus Naked Skin® designed by Braun
data.description:
Gillette Venus Naked Skin® designed by Braun is an intense pulsed light hair removal system that has been clinically tested for at-home use. In other words, you'll get professionally derived intense pulsed light technology at a fraction of the cost.  

With continued, periodic use, the light energy helps prevent unwanted hair from reaching the skin's surface. How often or when do you treat with Naked Skin®IPL?  

During the Start Up phase, treat once every two weeks for 6 - 12 treatments. After the Start Up phase, just treat once every two months to maintain Continuously Smooth skin. Maintaining beautiful skin just got a whole lot easier.

data.title: How to Use Gillette Venus Naked Skin® IPL designed by Braun
data.description:
Introducing Gillette Venus Naked Skin® designed by Braun Intense Pulsed Light Hair Removal System. Help break the cycle of hair re-growth with Gillette Venus Naked Skin® in these four simple steps.  

1. Shave the area you wish to treat.  
2. Liberally apply an even layer of V Activating Gel.   
3.Treat the area with Gillette Venus Naked Skin®. During the Start Up phase, treat once every two weeks for 6 - 12 treatments.   
4. After the Start Up phase, just treat once every two months to maintain Continuously Smooth skin.  

Maintaining beautiful skin just got a whole lot easier.
